    {
      "id": "gJ79LeobkV3kiUXoAj8qe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 153.27688598632812,
      "y": 1613.3701580056459,
      "width": 813.95947265625,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aW",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1550629260,
      "version": 40,
      "versionNonce": 87874100,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781065663071,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "LangSmith is a debugging, monitoring, and evaluation platform for applications built \nwith LLMs and AI agents. It is made by the LangChain team, but it can \nalso work with applications that do not use LangChain.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LangSmith is a debugging, monitoring, and evaluation platform for applications built \nwith LLMs and AI agents. It is made by the LangChain team, but it can \nalso work with applications that do not use LangChain.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zvTj7fjaBm7RH3NsWU5TB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 145.13882446289062,
      "y": 1726.842385945499,
      "width": 759.1194458007812,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aX",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1274726196,
      "version": 52,
      "versionNonce": 1764046772,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781065583840,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Why it is useful?\n\nWhen your chatbot receives a question, several hidden operations may happen:",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Why it is useful?\n\nWhen your chatbot receives a question, several hidden operations may happen:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2lVuEI1COrYZ3HU_1Agsl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 249.24038696289062,
      "y": 1834.5181040322366,
      "width": 378.41986083984375,
      "height": 385,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aY",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 67767988,
      "version": 94,
      "versionNonce": 1910596916,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781065570672,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "User question\n   ↓\nPrompt construction\n   ↓\nLLM call\n   ↓\nTool or database call\n   ↓\nMemory/checkpoint retrieval\n   ↓\nFinal response",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "User question\n   ↓\nPrompt construction\n   ↓\nLLM call\n   ↓\nTool or database call\n   ↓\nMemory/checkpoint retrieval\n   ↓\nFinal response",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "nPGBSPwY8YaUoJzkl0_-W",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 176.11758422851562,
      "y": 2313.71879756451,
      "width": 1255.267333984375,
      "height": 420,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aZ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1489853068,
      "version": 22,
      "versionNonce": 1431720244,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781065642712,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "LangSmith records this complete execution as a trace, allowing you to inspect every step, \nincluding inputs, outputs, errors, execution time, token usage, tool calls, and model behavior.\n\nFor your LangGraph Agentic chatbot, LangSmith can help you:\n\n👉🏻Find why an agent selected the wrong tool.\n👉🏻Inspect the exact prompt sent to the model.\n👉🏻Debug failed nodes in the LangGraph workflow.\n👉🏻Measure response latency and token costs.\n👉🏻Review conversations and multi-turn threads.\n👉🏻Compare different prompts or model versions.\n👉🏻Evaluate chatbot quality before and after deployment.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LangSmith records this complete execution as a trace, allowing you to inspect every step, \nincluding inputs, outputs, errors, execution time, token usage, tool calls, and model behavior.\n\nFor your LangGraph Agentic chatbot, LangSmith can help you:\n\n👉🏻Find why an agent selected the wrong tool.\n👉🏻Inspect the exact prompt sent to the model.\n👉🏻Debug failed nodes in the LangGraph workflow.\n👉🏻Measure response latency and token costs.\n👉🏻Review conversations and multi-turn threads.\n👉🏻Compare different prompts or model versions.\n👉🏻Evaluate chatbot quality before and after deployment.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
